'''Luis Alberto Coppola Joffroy''' (born 29 May 1948) is a [[Mexican people|Mexican]] politician affiliated with the [[National Action Party (Mexico)|PAN]]. He served as Senator of the [[LX Legislature of the Mexican Congress|LX]] and [[LXI Legislature of the Mexican Congress|LXI]] Legislatures of the Mexican Congress representing [[Baja California Sur]].<ref>{{cite web|title=Perfil del legislador|url=http://sil.gobernacion.gob.mx/Librerias/pp_PerfilLegislador.php?SID=&Referencia=2303978|publisher=Legislative Information System|accessdate=25 September 2013}}</ref>
